85,9.30667,435.17162,4.3517162,6.066572080228944,1.332807502474541,472.6870745845053,0.4595887939567382,'D','medium','low','medium','medium',7,'chicken','1.cornstarch,2.water,3.minced garlic,4.minced fresh ginger root,5.white sugar,6.soy sauce,7.white wine vinegar,8.hot chicken broth,9.monosodium glutamate (MSG),10.skinless, boneless chicken breast halves, cut into bite size pieces,11.soy sauce,12.ground white pepper,13.egg,14.cornstarch,15.vegetable oil,16.chopped green onions,17.chile peppers, sun-dried');
